'''GW150914'''是由[[激光干涉引力波天文台|激光干涉引力波天文台]]（LIGO）于2015年9月14日探测到的引力波现象，是人类首次直接探测到的引力波。相关探测结果由LIGO、[[處女座干涉儀|處女座干涉儀]]（Virgo）研究团队于2016年2月11日共同宣布。这束产生于双黑洞的引力波信号与广义相对论中对[[双黑洞|双黑洞]]旋近、併合以及併合后的黑洞会发生衰荡（{{lang-en|ringdown}}）的理论预测相符。同时GW150914也是人类对双黑洞併合的首度观测，展示了双黑洞系统确实存在，且其併合在宇宙的目前阶段仍能发生。<ref name="PRL-20160211">{{cite journal|language=en|first1=B. P.|last1=Abbott|author2=et al. (LIGO Scientific Collaboration and Virgo Collaboration)|title=Observation of Gravitational Waves from a Binary Black Hole Merger|journal=Physical Review Letters|volume=116|pages=061102|year=2016|doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.116.061102|url=http://journals.aps.org/prl/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevLett.116.061102|access-date=2016-02-11|archive-date=2019-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191025233058/https://journals.aps.org/prl/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevLett.116.061102|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYT-20160212">{{cite news |language=en |last=Overbye |first=D. |title=Physicists Detect Gravitational Waves, Proving Einstein Right |work=New York Times |date=2016-02-12 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/12/science/ligo-gravitational-waves-black-holes-einstein.html |archivedate=2016-02-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160215195605/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/12/science/ligo-gravitational-waves-black-holes-einstein.html |accessdate=2016-02-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name='Clark 2016'>{{cite news |language=en |title=Gravitational waves: scientists announce 'we did it!' – live |work=The Guardian |archivedate=2016-02-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216095206/https://www.theguardian.com/science/across-the-universe/live/2016/feb/11/gravitational-wave-announcement-latest-physics-einstein-ligo-black-holes-live |url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/across-the-universe/live/2016/feb/11/gravitational-wave-announcement-latest-physics-einstein-ligo-black-holes-live |date=2016-02-11 |accessdate=2016-02-11 |first=S. |last=Clark |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Nature_11Feb16">{{cite news |